long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get ready to unleash your inner luchador! With the Burrito Bison Chrome extension, you can dive right into the wild, candy-coated world of Burrito Bison, where you’ll be catapulted through hordes of gummy bears, break through barriers, and chase freedom from the sticky clutches of Candy Land! 🥳💥

Why Install This Extension?
Instant Gameplay: Start playing Burrito Bison instantly in your browser—no downloads, no fuss. Just pure, arcade-style fun at your fingertips!
Addictive Action: Launch, smash, and upgrade with each run. The addictive physics and hilarious gameplay will keep you coming back for more!
Powerful Upgrades: Collect coins and unlock abilities that boost your speed, bounce, and power for longer and higher launches! 🚀💪
Achievements & Challenges: Reach milestones, discover new strategies, and conquer challenges to become the ultimate luchador hero.

Features:
Accessible Gameplay: Play directly from the extension—just open, launch, and start smashing through gummy foes.
Perfect for Quick Breaks: Enjoy a fun and quick game whenever you need to unwind or take a break.
No Internet Needed: Once installed, Burrito Bison runs right in your browser without requiring a connection. 🌐

How to Play
Pull back the slingshot and launch Burrito Bison!
Aim for gummy bears to maintain speed and bounce.
Upgrade your abilities to soar further, smash harder, and reach the end of Candy Land.
Aim for those gummy foes to boost your distance—higher launches mean more coins and bigger upgrades! 🤑💰
With Burrito Bison, you’re not just playing a game; you’re smashing your way through the sweetest escape adventure! Install the extension and join Burrito Bison’s quest to escape Candy Land today!

Play more games on the top-left menu.
